### FastAPI Document Processing API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

###############################################
# Health Check / Root Endpoint
###############################################

### Get root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

###############################################
# Document Processing Endpoints
###############################################

### Process documents - Single PDF file
POST {{baseUrl}}/process-documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="BL-COSU534343282.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./tests/doc/BL-COSU534343282.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Process documents - Single Excel file
POST {{baseUrl}}/process-documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="Demo-Invoice-PackingList_1.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

